item.title: Help with making a place in safe zone?
item.dc:creator: @Xile_Maizez Xile Maizez
item.description:
@Xile_Maizez wrote:

client.java, CTRL + F, search for:

nonWild

Under it, copy and paste one of the long sentances.
Change the first number to the NORTH WEST X COORD.
Change the Second Number to the SOUTH EAST X COORD.
Change the Third Number to the SOUTH EAST Y COORD.
Change the Fourth Number to the NORTH WEST Y COORD.

Sorry if its confusing =.
